sobre ello.

137
00:08:26,244 --> 00:08:27,679
¿En serio?

138
00:08:29,430 --> 00:08:32,009
Has leí demasiadas novelas.

139
00:08:59,770 --> 00:09:00,950
¡Hola!

140
00:09:01,562 --> 00:09:02,545
Me pone nervioso

141
