223
00:14:16,794 --> 00:14:17,746
¿Edward?

224
00:14:19,330 --> 00:14:20,198
¿Edward?

225
00:14:32,945 --> 00:14:33,956
Cielos

226
00:14:35,488 --> 00:14:36,493
Srta. Austen

227
00:14:37,332 --> 00:14:38,523
